---
title: Plant-Based Chick'n Tenders & Wedges with Burger Sauce & Avocado Salad
description: A plant-based version of chick'n tenders, yes it can be done. A side of golden wedges to dip in a burger sauce (it’s great for the
chick'n tenders too!) will make your mouth water in no time.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/672383d606f5566883435ebb-ded4517b.jpeg
